parameters:
\nc<Saki>Ah, that's right. My first day of work is coming up soon. I
need to contact my employer...

\nc<Saki>I'm sorry for the sudden call. Actually, it seems I've
become a succubus...
\nc<Saki>Ah, no, I'm not joking, it's true.
\nc<Director>Then, that means we'll have to rescind your job offer.

\nc<Director>Succubi are known for being perverts among the demon kind. I
can't entrust our children to someone like that.

\nc<Saki>He-Hello? Hello!? You've got to be kidding... The line's
dead!
\nc<Saki>I need to find another job quickly...
